flowchart TD
    %% Spec Lifecycle — proposal to locked spec

    REQ([Feature Request]) --> TRIAGE{Complexity Triage<br/>Tiny / Standard / Complex}
    TRIAGE --> DOM{Domain spec<br/>exists?}
    DOM -- Yes --> READ[Read domain spec<br/>anchor to current behavior]
    DOM -- No --> GRILL
    READ --> GRILL[Grilling Waves<br/>Wave 1: Problem & Scope<br/>Wave 2: Behavior & Decisions<br/>Wave 3: Risk & Verification]

    GRILL --> CONFLICT{Contradictory<br/>answers?}
    CONFLICT -- Yes --> RESOLVE[Name conflict<br/>present tradeoff<br/>lock decision]
    RESOLVE --> GRILL
    CONFLICT -- No --> PROP[proposal.md<br/>high-level alignment]

    PROP --> ALIGN{User aligned?}
    ALIGN -- No --> GRILL
    ALIGN -- Yes --> SCOPE[Scope Cut<br/>In / Out / Non-Goals]
    SCOPE --> AUTHOR[Author spec.md<br/>REQ + AC + Verification Surface]
    AUTHOR --> GRAY[Lock Gray-Area Decisions<br/>in spec.md]
    GRAY --> REVIEW[optional requirements-review.md<br/>6-dimension readiness score]

    REVIEW --> SCORE{Score >= 19/30?}
    SCORE -- No --> AUTHOR
    SCORE -- Yes --> LOCK([Spec Locked<br/>status = Spec Approved])

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#fff7ed,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef step fill:#fff,stroke:#10a37f,color:#0d0d0d,stroke-width:1.5px
    classDef loop fill:#fcf3f3,stroke:#f2c4c4,color:#c62828

    class REQ,LOCK terminal
    class TRIAGE,DOM,CONFLICT,ALIGN,SCORE decision
    class READ,GRILL,PROP,SCOPE,AUTHOR,GRAY,REVIEW step
    class RESOLVE loop
